nodes.text: Qi'ra's safe house was a ship used as a secret safe house by the scrumrat Qi'ra in the freighter boneyard in Coronet City on the planet Corellia. Whilst Qi'ra, Han and Tsuulo were on the run from the White Worms, Kaldana Syndicate, and Droid Gotra after obtaining a datacube from TD-H4, the trio sought refuge in Qi'ra's safe house.
